      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUPER BATMAN (8) has a strong record here with three wins and two placings from eight starts. Below best last time at The Meadows (30.76) in a Grade 5 FIN, finishing a 4.5 lengths fifth. Makes strong appeal on best. BIT OF POTASH (5) was a strong winner (26.02) from box 8 last time, scoring by 3 lengths at this track. Has the squeeze box to overcome and will need the breaks early. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Form should stack up. VALLETTA PEARL (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (26.02) at Shepparton behind Sunny Stride in a Grade 5. Chased the leaders and with a clean run can be prominent. Expected to be in this for a long way. ZIPPING CARDI (2) cannot be left out despite coming off a short break.",
